flowchart TD
    start([Start service info]) --> getService[Get service argument]
    getService --> loadConfig[ServiceManager getService]
    loadConfig --> loadTemplate[ServiceTemplateLoader load]
    loadTemplate --> checkFound{Config or template exists?}
    checkFound -->|no| notFound[Error - service not found]
    checkFound -->|yes| output{JSON output?}
    output -->|yes| jsonOutput[Output JSON with all info]
    output -->|no| renderInfo[Render detailed info]
    renderInfo --> showTemplate[Show template info]
    showTemplate --> showConfig[Show current configuration]
    showConfig --> showSchema[Show available options]
